dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Clark County, Wisconsin in 2023. [It is the public road centerline layer but also contains private driveways that are longer in length. Road classes are identified for each centerline-only primary forest roads are included in this layer. Additional forest roads are maintained in a separate layer maintained by the Forestry Department. The data is updated when mistakes are found or when information is provided by the owning entity.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
